what we see being a reflection of what is going on in the inside... such a fascinating thing. Our moods and feelings can definitely be expressed through colour... but also hide what we don't want others to see. I am in awe again and again when I realise how much we communicate to others, even when we don't want to. 
This also goes to say that it is a skill worth having in my opinion. I see the healing/ therapeutic potential in having a good grasp over colours too!
